    // ...
    <Button
       isLoading={login.isPending} // Data originates here
       type="submit"
       className="w-full"
    >
      Log in
    </Button>
    // ...
  );
};
```

The `useLogin` hook is imported from `@/lib/auth`. It is a mutation hook (likely a TanStack Query `useMutation` wrapper) where `isPending` tracks the loading state of the login request.

