---

## All Props Accepted by `PostList`

**File:** `components/post_view/post_list/post_list.tsx`

The `Props` interface defines the following props:

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `formattedPostIds` | `string[]` | Optional | Array of **formatted/grouped** post IDs (with date separators, "new messages" markers, etc.). Passed directly to `VirtPostList`. |
| `postListIds` | `string[]` | Optional | Array of **raw post IDs** ordered newest-to-oldest. Used internally for oldest/latest ID lookups and to decide whether to show a loading screen. |
