| `channelId` | `string` | **Required** | The ID of the channel whose posts are being displayed. |
| `focusedPostId` | `string` | Optional | Used to load posts around a specific post (permalink view). |
| `atLatestPost` | `boolean` | **Required** | Whether the current chunk includes the most recent post in the channel. |
